latestPosts.caption:
“Mardon Wali Baat”—A Journey of Reflection & Change

Being part of the Mardon Wali Baat campaign has been an eye-opening experience. It made me question, unlearn, and redefine what masculinity truly means. From deep conversations at the Cequin retreat to understanding the privilege I carry, this journey has been about reimagining masculinity in a way that’s not about dominance, but about equality, empathy, and strength in kindness.

I was honored to be a panelist representing fashion and lifestyle influencers at the panel discussion on March 19th at India Habitat Centre. It was a powerful space to share my views on the campaign and discuss how the industry can contribute to breaking stereotypes and redefining masculinity.

The campaign led to impactful discussions, and now, it all comes together with the launch of Mardangi Reloaded: Challenging Notions of Toxic Masculinities—a film that urges us to rethink societal norms.

👉 Watch here: https://youtu.be/xM6iFIypLiE

#MardonWaliBaat #CEQUIN #MardangiReloaded #ReimaginingMasculinities #GenderEquality
